---
import Layout from '../layouts/TamilLitLayout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Minor Classics (Pathinenkilkanakku)">
  <div class="tamil-lit-wrapper">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title"><span class="tamil-text">பதினெண்கீழ்க்கணக்கு</span> Minor Classics</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">The Eighteen Didactic Texts</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="prose">
          <p>Following the Sangam period, during the Kalabhra interregnum, a new corpus of literature emerged focusing heavily on ethics, morality, and asceticism. Thirukkural and Naladiyar are the most famous of these eighteen texts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
